NOTES:
This file demonstrates the NEW bend format with step amounts.

SECTION 1 - BASIC BENDS (8 beats):
  Beat 1: 7b{½} = Half-step bend at fret 7
  Beat 2: 7b{1} = Whole-step bend at fret 7
  Beat 3: 7b{1½} = 1.5-step bend at fret 7
  Beat 4: 7b{2} = 2-step bend at fret 7

SECTION 2 - BEND & RELEASE (8 beats):
  Beat 1: 7b{1}r = Whole-step bend with release
  Beat 2: 7b{½}r = Half-step bend with release
  Beat 3: 7b{1½}r = 1.5-step bend with release

SECTION 3 - PRE-BEND (8 beats):
  Beat 1: pb{1}7 = Pre-bend 1 step at fret 7
  Beat 2: pb{½}7 = Pre-bend ½ step at fret 7
  Beat 3: pb{1½}7 = Pre-bend 1½ step at fret 7
  Beat 4: pb{1}7r = Pre-bend 1 step with release

SECTION 4 - MIXED WITH PICKING (8 beats):
  Bends combined with picking notation

DISPLAY SYMBOLS:
  ↗½   = Bend half-step
  ↗1   = Bend whole-step
  ↗1½  = Bend 1.5 steps
  ↗1↘  = Bend with release
  ᵇ1   = Pre-bend 1 step
  ᵇ1↘  = Pre-bend with release

LEGEND:
New Bend Format:
  7b{1}    = Bend 1 step at fret 7
  7b{½}    = Bend ½ step at fret 7
  7b{1½}   = Bend 1½ step at fret 7
  7b{1}r   = Bend 1 step, release back
  pb{1}7   = Pre-bend 1 step at fret 7
  pb{1}7r  = Pre-bend 1 step, release

Finger & Picking:
  (f3)     = Finger 3
  (f3:d)   = Finger 3 + down pick
  (d)      = Down pick only
